General.Name: Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret AS
General.Description: Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi distributes information technology consumables in Turkey and internationally. It offers toners, cartridges, ribbon, back up products, side components, accessories, paper products, mobile phones, etc. The company offers its products to computer companies and office supply stores. Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
